nodes.text: Clone Corporal was a rank held by clone troopers during the Clone Wars. Comet was a Clone Corporal by the Second Battle of Felucia, as was ARC trooper CT-1409 "Echo," who was promoted to the rank in the aftermath of the Battle of Anaxes. Kaylon, Mixx, and Big-Mouth were corporals in a battalion commanded by Depa Billaba.
